    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle is offered in impeccable condition, having been preserved to showroom standards with exhaustive attention to detail. Both its aesthetic presentation and mechanical performance are beyond reproach, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of investment-grade quality. Experience a level of refinement and integrity that is indistinguishable from its original manufacture.",
